ream solar wind data is\navailable. However, during the main phase of major storms, residuals\n(observed-modeled) are found to be large, suggesting influence of internal\nfactors such as magnetospheric processes\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 Mar 2017 17:31:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-19"}
