. The data reported were\nobtained using a variety of analytic techniques. The measurement sensitivities\nare among the best in the field. Construction of the EXO-200 detector has been\nconcluded, and Phase-I data was taken from 2011 to 2014. The detector's\nextremely low background implicitly verifies the measurements and the analysis\nassumptions made during construction and reported in this paper.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 31 Mar 2017 08:42:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-03-14"}
